    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>웹페이지를 스타일링 하다보면</p>\n<p>여러가지 테마를 적용하고 싶을때가 있다</p>\n<p>예를들어 Dark모드와 Light모드가 있다</p>\n<p>이럴때 styled-components를 사용하면 간편하게 스타일링이 가능하다</p>\n<p>해당 프로젝트는 TypeScript를 사용하므로 아래와같이 프로젝트를 생성하여 적용해보자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">yarn create react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app theme<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>management <span class=\"token operator\">--</span>template typescript</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"1-themets생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-themets%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 themets생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. theme.ts생성</h1>\n<p>src폴더 아래에 theme.ts 생성</p>\n<p>전역적으로 가져다쓸 테마의 핵심이되는 스타일을 정의해주는 부분이다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* theme.ts */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> DefaultTheme <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">darkTheme</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> DefaultTheme <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bgColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"black\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">textColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"white\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">lightTheme</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> DefaultTheme <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bgColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"white\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">textColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"black\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"2-styleddts-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-styleddts-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"2 styleddts 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. styled.d.ts 생성</h1>\n<p>src폴더 아래에 styled.d.ts생성</p>\n<p>theme.ts에서 모든 테마에서 하나도 빠짐없이 구현해야하는 모든 스타일값을 정의해주는</p>\n<p>DefaultTheme 인터페이스를 styled.d.ts에 적어주자</p>\n<p>dark테마와 light테마 모두 DefaultTheme 인터페이스를 상속시켜주자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* styled.d.ts */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\ndeclare module <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DefaultTheme</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">textColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bgColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"3-themeprovider로-감싸주기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-themeprovider%EB%A1%9C-%EA%B0%90%EC%8B%B8%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"3 themeprovider로 감싸주기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. ThemeProvider로 감싸주기</h1>\n<p>전역적으로 사용될 컴포넌트들의 부모에</p>\n<p>styled-components에서 제공하는 ThemeProvider로 한번 감싸주면</p>\n<p>하위 컴포넌트에서 언제든지 theme의 스타일에 접근이 가능하다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* App.tsx */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> App <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRoot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> HTMLElement\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nroot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>App <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* App.tsx */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ThemeProvider <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> darkTheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lightTheme <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./theme\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> App <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> root <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ReactDOM<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createRoot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"root\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> HTMLElement\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nroot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ThemeProvider theme<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>darkTheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Test <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ThemeProvider<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>StrictMode<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"3-1-recoil을-사용한-간편한-테마전환\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-1-recoil%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C-%EA%B0%84%ED%8E%B8%ED%95%9C-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88%EC%A0%84%ED%99%98\" aria-label=\"3 1 recoil을 사용한 간편한 테마전환 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-1. Recoil을 사용한 간편한 테마전환</h1>\n<p>테마를 어느 컴포넌트에서나 접근하여 변경하려면</p>\n<p>Recoil과 같은 상태관리 라이브러리를 사용하는것이 편리하다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* App.tsx */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react-dom/client\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> ThemeProvider <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> darkTheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> lightTheme <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./theme\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useRecoilValue <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"recoil\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> isDarkAtom <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./atoms\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Test <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./Test\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> isDark <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useRecoilValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>isDarkAtom<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ThemeProvider theme<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>isDark <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> darkTheme <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> lightTheme<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Test <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ThemeProvider<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* atoms.ts */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> atom <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"recoil\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> isDarkAtom <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">atom</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">key</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"isDark\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"4-테마-스타일-적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88-%EC%8A%A4%ED%83%80%EC%9D%BC-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"4 테마 스타일 적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 테마 스타일 적용하기</h1>\n<p>ThemeProvider로 감싸줬으면 하위 컴포넌트에서</p>\n<p>스타일을 가져다 사용해보자</p>\n<p>styled-components의 createGlobalStyle에 스타일을 적용하면</p>\n<p>해당 컴포넌트 및 하위컴포넌트에 전역적으로 스타일링이 적용된다</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Test.tsx */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> createGlobalStyle <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"styled-components\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> GlobalStyle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> createGlobalStyle<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\r\n  body {\r\n    background-color: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bgColor<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">;\r\n    color: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textColor<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">;\r\n  }\r\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n       <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>GlobalStyle<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>GlobalStyle<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"간편하게 테마 스타일링 하는법","summary":"styled-components와 Recoil을 사용하여 간편하게 테마별 스타일링을 해보자","date":"2022.05.19.","categories":["CSS","Recoil"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/e018d/styled-components.png","srcSet":"/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/c6b60/styled-components.png 480w,\n/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/f5e84/styled-components.png 960w,\n/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/e018d/styled-components.png 1920w","sizes":"(min-width: 1920px) 1920px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/0df1a/styled-components.webp 480w,\n/static/cb78c7c0c433a92837be6cf66cfc87de/eeb31/styled-components.webp 960w,\n/static/